Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.38,0:00:31.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please come to the rooftop of the school's \Nsouth building after school on April 28th.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.18,0:00:32.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Signed, Souma Sumire.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.84,0:00:37.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tomoki, there's a pretty \Nstrange girl in your class, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,A strange girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.72,0:00:42.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! You mean that weird chick with long hair.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.19,0:00:43.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's kinda like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.69,0:00:44.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Like me?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.87,0:00:47.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She hardly ever talks and always\N has this blank look on her face.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's like she's not interested in anyone around her.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.29,0:00:51.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Her name's Haruki Misora.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.94,0:00:55.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, I'd say I'm pretty\N talkative and expressive.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And my name is Asai Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.99,0:00:59.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's so similar about us?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.51,0:01:00.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere around you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.18,0:01:03.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's like you both lack genuine feeling\N whenever you do something.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.34,0:01:05.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that how you see it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hell, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.65,0:01:15.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So, what's this about Haruki?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.88,0:01:19.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's not the one I wanted to ask you about.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.64,0:01:22.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's Souma Sumire. \NYou know, the one with short hair.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the class rep of my class.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.14,0:01:27.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've talked to her a few times.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.30,0:01:30.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And earlier today, I found a letter in my shoe locker.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.51,0:01:33.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It said she wants to meet me \Non the rooftop tomorrow after school.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.74,0:01:37.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's totally gonna ask you out! \NSo, whatcha gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.21,0:01:38.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I have no reason to refuse her invitation.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.51,0:01:44.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You see, that's a perfect example \Nof how you simply go with the flow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're in Class 2-1, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.54,0:02:16.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to know Souma?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She told me to meet her up here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you know where she might be?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.69,0:02:31.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's your favorite food?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's your least favorite food?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.12,0:02:38.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you think we're alike?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It depends on your definition of "alike."
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,By the way, why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.94,0:02:47.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you want to be left alone, I can just leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.60,0:02:50.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm here because Souma Sumire\N told me to come here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to be alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.92,0:02:58.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd said that when I brought Souma up.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you talk to her often?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.00,0:03:07.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The classmate I talked to the most when\N I was a first-year was Souma Sumire.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.23,0:03:09.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you {\i1}are{\i0} close.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.23,0:03:14.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're already becoming the person I've \Ntalked to most since I became a second-year.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Reset.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.13,0:04:18.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you ask me, I'd say I'm pretty\N talkative and expressive.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And my name is Asai Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's so similar about us?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere around you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's like you both lack genuine feeling\N whenever you do something.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we do.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hell, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So, what's this about Haruki?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.85,0:04:41.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Uh... Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing. I was just thinking\N I didn't have much of a chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.14,0:04:52.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This place is called Sakurada. \NIt's a town tucked away in Japan,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.26,0:04:55.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,where about half of the people\N possess special abilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There are a vast range of abilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.58,0:05:02.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,While they generally defy the laws of physics, \Nthey are pretty much useless for the most part.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.84,0:05:07.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There's a reason why people\N with abilities live in Sakurada:
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.55,0:05:12.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If someone leaves Sakurada, \Nthey end up forgetting about their ability.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.48,0:05:17.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Being unaware of an ability you can use\N is no different from not having one at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.72,0:05:23.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I possess the ability to relive the past\N in my mind with all five senses.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.41,0:05:29.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I can always remember the things I've seen,\N heard, and thought with absolute accuracy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.52,0:05:34.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So far, my ability has only been effective enough\N to say that I've got a better memory than others.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, where should we go?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.49,0:05:41.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The place we went to last time!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.78,GJM_Overlap_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Asai.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Souma?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Doing my class rep duties.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.10,0:06:02.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In a place like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.83,0:06:05.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter where I do them.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,As long as it isn't on the rooftop\N of the south building.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.18,0:06:12.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a bit rude when you ask me\N to come somewhere and then not show up at all?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.76,0:06:17.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it part of the class rep's duties\N to set me and Haruki up?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have any friends she's close with.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.93,0:06:23.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I just simply thought that if I have \Nyou two meet, you'd become friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.80,0:06:28.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll try, but I don't think it's possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We're not compatible at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Like you wouldn't believe.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.14,0:06:36.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why me, of all people?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Because you're compatible.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You two are really alike.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're identical in how you \Nboth lead very proper lives.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Not in that we both lack genuine feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.54,0:06:51.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you ever wanna get closer to Haruki, \NI don't mind helping you out.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is there any real point to that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.44,0:06:59.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There is. There's a huge meaning\N to you two being together.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Like, say for example, resetting.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Reset.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this is the second time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is resetting your ability?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.92,0:07:21.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I can restore the world to as far as three days back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So you can basically rewind time?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.11,0:07:30.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No. I just rearrange everything to its past state.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.26,0:07:35.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Since I rearrange things, \NI strictly reconstruct the world of the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So it's not as if you're erasing time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's really just a reset.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.36,0:07:44.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even human brain cells get\N rearranged to their past state.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.22,0:07:47.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Because of that, people lose\N their memories of that time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.44,0:07:48.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.86,0:07:52.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,However, my ability has three restrictions to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.16,0:07:57.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,First of all, I can't use my ability \Nto reset if I didn't save beforehand.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.22,0:08:00.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The save expires after 72 hours.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.75,0:08:06.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Secondly, I can't save until 24 hours\N have passed since a reset.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.71,0:08:10.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So basically, you can't repeat \Nthe same time over and over again.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.43,0:08:14.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And lastly, the biggest restriction out of the three:
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,resetting personally affects me, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,All my memories of that time also disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.48,0:08:23.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even the memory of the reset itself disappears.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.17,0:08:28.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Spring is almost over.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Summer starts next weekend.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.32,0:08:35.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Summer is always \Nmuch sooner than you think.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.52,0:08:40.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's spend our summer here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.41,0:08:43.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We can meet up as much as we want
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,and talk about all sorts of things that can \Nhelp us understand each other better.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is there any point in doing that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who cares if there's a point or not?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.31,0:08:57.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll just be hanging out like sparrows that \Nare only on a power line to rest their wings.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't like doing things without any purpose.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.89,0:09:07.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then, let's assume there's an android among us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,An android?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They look just like humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.92,0:09:14.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if you were to hold their hand, \Nkiss them, or check their blood,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't know that they're artificial.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.48,0:09:20.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So, who among us is that kind of android?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's the point of this?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's just a simple question.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who's an android?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We're all just ordinary humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.80,0:09:33.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just think about it. \NWho would you expect to be an android?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.46,0:09:37.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's make figuring \Nthat out a reason to meet up.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.12,0:09:40.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And then, at the end of summer, \Nwe'll tell each other our answers.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Resetting, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's an interesting ability, but it's not very useful.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You simply experience the same time period twice.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,On top of that, you're not aware\N that it's the second time.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Normally.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.18,0:09:55.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It seems like resetting doesn't affect my memory.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think my special ability preserves it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.45,0:10:09.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Until now, I sometimes had this feeling as if \Nmy memory and sense of time were doubled.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.66,0:10:12.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think it might have something \Nto do with Haruki's reset ability.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.87,0:10:16.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You should totally reset after memorizing \Nthe winning lottery ticket numbers!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll do that when I'm completely \Ndesperate for money.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Totally saw that coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.26,0:10:24.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You always take the high road.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure it can be used for good.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It might break the rules of this world, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.63,0:10:36.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Reset.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't have a save.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to know my mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Where did you lose sight of her?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.89,0:10:57.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what you've been doing up until now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.44,0:11:00.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was at the hospital for a checkup.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please tell me your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kurakawa Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please let go.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's work together.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.82,0:11:37.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Together?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.10,0:11:41.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I won't lose my memory even\N if you use your reset ability.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So if we team up, we can redo the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We can overcome any problem together.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.79,0:11:49.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Because I abide by the rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Rules?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a guideline for me to decide on things.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,For instance,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.51,0:12:01.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,if it has a probability of causing a negative\N effect on my surroundings, I refuse to reset.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.36,0:12:04.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Will it cause a negative effect if we work together?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a possibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.55,0:12:07.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.69,0:12:11.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Because you're the only one\N who can exploit resetting.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.46,0:12:14.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When I do a reset, I lose my memory of that time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.68,0:12:17.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even notice your lies.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You have too much initiative in this situation.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.39,0:12:24.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Plus, I don't have any basis to trust you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Haruki.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.64,0:12:31.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You used your reset ability on this rooftop\N after school on April 28th, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes. Probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm curious why you did it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It was probably because a girl was crying.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.66,0:12:43.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Whenever I see someone crying, I reset.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's pointless.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if you reset, she'll end up crying anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.28,0:12:52.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It being pointless isn't a reason\N for breaking the rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.83,0:13:00.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Haruki...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.76,0:13:06.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'll be able to earn your trust in due time.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.53,0:13:10.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Not once have I ever trusted anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Then, I'll be the first.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you two warm up to each other?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't say. It's kinda difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.52,0:13:25.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh? So even you can admit when things are difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I started to wonder if she truly had anything to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.03,0:13:32.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kei, why do you want to get closer to Haruki?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,To get my hands on her reset ability.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.91,0:13:40.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kei, you're the kind of person that always gives\N self-deprecating answers to such questions.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's caused by your extremely\N strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.75,0:13:46.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's on the same level \Nas clean-freaks or perfectionists.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.18,0:13:49.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm that righteous.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.02,0:13:54.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,God once placed a curse on one young man.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.54,0:13:59.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It was a curse that shot pain throughout the man's \Nentire body when he came across a sad person.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow... That sounds terrible.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.57,0:14:06.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In order to avoid his pain, the young man\N reached out to all the sad people.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.08,0:14:12.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,God then made a copy of the \Nyoung man and created a fake.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.35,0:14:17.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The copy had no will of its own, \Nso it did the same thing the original did.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.06,0:14:21.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The fake also reached out to all the sad people.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.47,0:14:25.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,God gave the two names of their own, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What kind of names?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.43,0:14:29.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,He chose the names Good and Hypocrisy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So who do you think got which name?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.64,0:14:36.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The real young man is Hypocrisy. The fake is Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The real one helps others for his own good.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.66,0:14:42.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't even have to think \Nabout who's genuinely good.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The fake is only following the real one's lead.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That isn't a problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Doing things for yourself isn't genuinely good.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.49,0:14:54.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That just shows how upright you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.16,0:14:58.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your sense of justice is so strong that \Nyou can't even admit you're righteous.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.44,0:15:02.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If there's even just a little bit of impurity within you, \Nyou'll end up thinking like you're a villain.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Haruki Misora is what you'd\N consider to be an ideal human.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.75,0:15:09.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's the only being that can be what \Nyou consider to be genuinely good.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.67,0:15:13.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's find out about Haruki's past.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.12,0:15:16.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We might find out how she \Nbecame the way that she is now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I know someone with the perfect ability for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think he'd probably be willing to help us out.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you usually do to have fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've been talking to this one person a lot lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Today, we talked about trust.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Trust?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It was about if it's possible \Nto accept a person's judgment
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,under circumstances when there's no logical basis.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.86,0:15:41.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,He said he would earn my trust.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So, that person likes you, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Likes?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.54,0:15:49.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I like you. And I like my mom, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.34,0:15:55.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But my mom doesn't like me. It's because I'm a fake.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "fake"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.56,0:16:04.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be liked by your mother?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.08,0:16:10.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm here to pick you up, Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who is this man?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,He's Mister Tsushima.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you Haruki?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.82,0:16:20.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard about you from Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She said you always spend time with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm like her stand-in guardian.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why isn't Mari's mother coming to pick her up?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She will. She's just a little late, that's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We need to get going, Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Where's Souma?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.03,0:16:46.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's meeting someone, so she'll apparently be late.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.69,0:16:55.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your hair's really pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.64,0:16:58.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And since it's pretty, it might be best to cut it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't get what you mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel real.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.74,0:17:06.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your pretty hair makes you \Nseem way too otherworldly.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.54,0:17:09.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai Kei, there's something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.88,0:17:18.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it sad to be unloved by your mother?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.39,0:17:23.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, it would normally be sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.17,0:17:25.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There's a girl named Kurakawa Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She wishes to be loved by her mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.85,0:17:31.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you know of a way to make that happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You want to help her, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.30,0:17:34.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.86,0:17:38.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I decided to be on her side.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.73,0:17:40.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Following your own rules?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.13,0:17:42.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.16,0:17:47.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you want to help that girl out \Nno matter what, then I'll help out.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.88,0:17:53.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But if you're helping the girl just for the sake of it,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,then I don't want to.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.80,0:17:59.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything to force you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kei! Haruki!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the student council room.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm the student\N council president, Sakagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,His ability is a pretty interesting one.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What? You haven't told them yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.33,0:18:14.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.44,0:18:19.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,B-Basically, my ability is copying the ability \Nof the person I'm touching with my right hand
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to the person I'm touching with my left.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.77,0:18:25.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I want you to copy Kei's ability of absolute memory to Haruki.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.94,0:18:28.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll make you remember your childhood times.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.71,0:18:29.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.63,0:18:33.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Because I wanna know. \NI'm really interested in your past.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so? All right, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.82,0:18:39.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Memories have tremendous power.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It might distort your personality, Haruki.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.12,0:18:45.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.42,0:18:51.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I understand. If there are any problems, let's reset.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.68,0:18:52.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Save.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.92,0:19:02.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If Asai uses his ability while we're like this, \NHaruki will get the same effect.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.99,0:19:05.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Haruki, what day do you want to remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.33,0:19:08.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well... Let's go back to when I was 5 years old.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'm starting now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was crying.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Always?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I cried very often...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.96,0:19:47.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Whenever I heard sad news, \Nor even if something broke.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why did you cry?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Because it was sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What was sad about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Everything about it was sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.56,0:19:59.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's sad that everyone will die someday.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.62,0:20:02.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's sad that everything will break someday.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.96,0:20:06.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Everything about those obvious rules is sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The natural way of things is sad, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.44,0:20:10.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.52,0:20:13.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's why you became unable to choose.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's why you created rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.52,0:20:21.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If anything and everything is tied to sadness, \Nthen there's no point in having choices.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No matter what you choose, it changes nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's why you became unable to choose.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.53,0:20:30.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You can't choose anything, and yet, \Nyou must choose something.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.61,0:20:33.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That is why you created rules for your own actions.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.97,0:20:34.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me one thing, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who's the one who's sad?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.60,0:20:50.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Haruki Misora, what you were \Nmissing was your sense of self.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.68,0:20:55.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The young Haruki didn't even realize \Nthat what she was sad about was herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If there wasn't any difference between \Na death you saw on TV and your own,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,then you wouldn't know how much \Nsadness there would be in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.96,0:21:09.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It must be very painful to live, feeling all the sadness\N of the world as if it affects you personally.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.10,0:21:13.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}After getting your feelings worn down by sadness, \Nyou become unable to do anything, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.37,0:21:16.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And yet, she still decided to keep going.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She created rules to make the right decisions.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She was forcing herself to try \Nand help even if she was unable to.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.88,0:21:27.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And to always make the right choices, \Neven if it meant losing her emotions.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.56,0:21:32.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think only Haruki, who doesn't have \Na sense of self, can remain righteous.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If there really is a person out \Nthere who we can call "Good,"
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'd be Haruki.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.14,0:21:41.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But Haruki isn't able to help anyone.{flashbacks in ep2, 03:13}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,People would rather get help, even from a hypocrite,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,than to be watched over by a good person.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.47,0:21:48.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.91,0:21:54.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Also, I think the ones who can save people\N are selfish hypocrites like you, Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no way. I'm not even a hypocrite.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.79,0:21:58.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.55,0:22:01.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're kind to a fault,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.59,0:22:04.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,and that uprightness of yours causes you\N to worry too much about your own malice.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.19,0:22:09.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're unable to believe that you're right,\N yet you continue to be righteous.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.01,0:22:10.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't get what you mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.69,0:22:13.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's prove it, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.88,0:22:15.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Prove it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.07,0:22:18.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll have you act as if you're a good person.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.96,0:22:28.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised. I wouldn't expect swings to suit you.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.50,0:22:31.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you really say that about swings?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.36,0:22:33.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Probably. They definitely don't suit me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.16,0:22:35.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're Kurakawa Mari, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.92,0:22:36.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.68,0:22:42.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Asai. \NI go to the same school as Haruki.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.94,0:22:44.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.82,0:22:45.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.48,0:22:52.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you know that a little girl named \NKurakawa Mari died seven years ago?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.66,0:22:55.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kurakawa Mari died seven years ago.{ep2, 00:01}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.50,0:22:56.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She died?{ep2, 00:03}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.56,0:23:01.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}When the doctor performed a C-section on Mari's \Nmother, Mari had already stopped breathing.{ep2, 00:04}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.15,0:23:08.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Mari, if Kurakawa Mari died, \Nthen who might you be?{ep2, 00:11}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.76,0:23:28.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You choose, Haruki.{ep2, 02:50}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you going to hand Mari over to the Bureau?{ep2, 02:52}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.42,0:23:32.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My job means doing things I don't want to do.{ep2, 02:39}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.55,0:23:33.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do with Haruki Misora?{ep2, 07:09}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.97,0:23:36.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I remembered all of the sadness \NI was supposed to feel soon.{ep2, 04:37}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.99,0:23:39.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go erase the girl's tears.{ep2, 04:43}
