Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:47.24,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\be3}We're always simply standing in a rain of eternal sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:54.74,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\be3}That is why I need that warmth of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:24:00.20,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H542024&\be3}Life is but a dream we never wake up from
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:08.28,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H542024&\be3}We repeat it over and over, praying for salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:13.86,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H542024&\be3}I kept waiting endlessly for your signal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.82,0:24:21.05,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H542024&\be3}To make sure you wouldn't disappear all by yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.60,0:24:25.56,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H9F5E46&\c&HFFFFFF&\be3}Ah, it doesn't matter where I am or what I'm doing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.56,0:24:29.28,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H9F5E46&\c&HFFFFFF&\be3}My heart can't go against your will
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.28,0:24:34.93,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H542024&\be3}So I'd follow you even to the ends of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.93,0:24:42.04,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H542024&\be3}I fell in love with you at the dawn of our new world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.04,0:24:48.67,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H542024&\be3}But we kept pushing the hand of the clock backwards
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.67,0:24:55.74,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H9F5E46&\c&HFFFFFF&\be3}And lost not only time, but our smiles as well
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.74,0:24:59.81,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H9F5E46&\c&HFFFFFF&\be3}You're the one who brought it back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.81,0:25:06.68,SagradaED1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\3c&H214B92&\c&HFFFFFF&\be3}And taught me that even lies can be meaningful
